  - {fileID: 21300000, guid: 6924da0c75abccf4786a097a8f05f30f, type: 3}
  firstSpeaker: Phone
  secondSpeaker: Ian
  dialogue:
  - You have two unread messages. First unheard message. *BEEP*
  - "*Ian, it's Wyatt.  I was cleaning up my place and think I found a record of
    yours? I must\u2019ve borrowed it from you and forgot to give it back haha. "
  - '*Anyways, let me know if you want to meet up so I can give it back and maybe
    we could catch up? Give me a call back. Later.'
  - '*End of message. Second unheard message. *BEEP*'
  - '*Hey Ian. I--'
  - There's no way in hell I'm listening to that. At least, not until I have some
    drinks in me and can barely remember her name.
  - No more messages. *BEEP*
  - Great. Time to actually start the day.
